query:
UPDATE vacant_shops 
SET mapMarkerX = NULL, mapMarkerY = NULL
WHERE id = (
  SELECT vs.id FROM vacant_shops vs
  JOIN shopping_centres c ON vs.centreId = c.id
  WHERE c.name = 'Eastgate Bondi Junction'
  LIMIT 1
);
